 python3-botocore (>= 1.37.4),
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
Description: Amazon S3 Transfer Manager (Avalan PPA transitive)
 s3transfer is a high-level transfer manager that boto3 uses for
 multipart uploads, range-based downloads, and copy operations.
 This package is built for the Avalan PPA because boto3 1.40.61
 (transitively required by aioboto3 in Avalan's `vendors` extra)
 pins s3transfer at `>= 0.14.0, < 0.15.0` while Noble ships
 0.10.1. Pinned at 0.14.0, the lowest version satisfying boto3's
 floor.
